package Part1
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    GraphSmoother
    The GraphSmoother class provides methods for smoothing a set of points using a moving window.
    Plotter
    The Plotter class provides methods for performing a mathematical function on values, This creates points based on the function within a specified range, and writes the points to a CSV file.
    Point
    The Point class represents a point object with an x and y value.
    Salter
    The Salter class provides methods for salting the y-values of points.
    TestGraphSmoother
    The TestGraphSmoother class serves as a test for the GraphSmoother functionality.
    TestPlotter
    The TestPlotter class serves as a test for the Plotter functionality.
    TestSalter
    The TestSalter class serves as a test for the Salter functionality.
